org.uutuc.util
Class JCasIterable

java.lang.Object
  org.uutuc.util.JCasIterable
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<JCas>, java.util.Iterator<JCas>
public class JCasIterable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<JCas>, java.lang.Iterable<JCas>

A class implementing iteration over a the documents of a collection. Each element in the Iterable is a JCas containing a single document. The documents have been loaded by the CollectionReader and processed by the AnalysisEngine (if any).

Author:
Steven Bethard, Philip Ogren
